## 13. v0.1 First-Build Objective

The first useful version needs to prove exactly one thing:

> A messy human idea can be reduced into a stable intermediate representation and re-emitted into multiple useful forms with visible preservation of core structure.

That alone is a meaningful artifact.

-----

## 14. Final Compression

If the entire engine had to be reduced to one sentence:

> The Pantheon Translation Engine converts ideas between representations by extracting invariants and rehydrating them into new forms without losing operative meaning.

Reduced further: **Meaning compiler.**

